high_descs: Turn right and move to the table in front of the window and to the left of the red garbage bin.
Pick up the spatula to the right of the head of lettuce on the table.
Move slightly to the left towards the door and look down at the table.
Place the spatula on the pan to the left of the fork on the table.
Pick up the pan containing the spatula from the table.
Turn right and move past the toaster and towards the range then turn left and face the kitchen counter.
Place the pan containing the spatula on the edge of the kitchen counter to the right of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Place a pan containing a spatula on the kitchen counter.

high_descs: go to the small white square table
grab the spatula off of the table
back up a bit and face the center of the table
put the spatula in the sauce pan on the table
pick up the sauce pan off of the table
walk over to the kitchen counter next to the toaster
place the sauce pan down on the counter
anns.task_desc: place a sauce pan with a spatula in it on the kitchen counter

high_descs: Turn to the right and walk forward to the blue table.
Pick up the spatula next to the head of lettuce.
Walk one step left and turn to face the pan on the table.
Place the spatula inside the pan on the table.
Pick up the pan on the table.
Turn right and walk forward, and then turn to the left and face the counter right after passing the toaster.
Place the pan down on the counter to the right of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Plan a pan with a spatula in it down on the counter to the right of the toaster.
